    - Add a bit of coconut oil (or another vegetable oil of your choice) to a pan on medium heat, pour 1 tbsp of the mixture in at a time. Flip once the bottoms have browned and little bubbles appear at the top.
    - Repeat for the rest of the pancake mix. 
