      Maple syrup : 1/2 tbsp
      Sea salt : 1 tsp
      Active dry yeast : 1 tsp
      All purpose flour : 2 1/4 cup
      Bamboo charcoal powder : 1 tsp
      Coconut oil : 2 tbsp
    Boiling water
      Water : 5 cups
      Baking soda : 1/3 cup 
    'egg' wash
      Soy milk : 1 tbsp
    Topping
      Fleur de sel : 1 tsp

