    & Candied peanuts inspired from <a href=\"http://www.thamilvirundhu.com/kadalai-urundai-peanut-chikki-thamil-virundhu/\">Kannathal's recipe</a>. She's got great tips for making desserts like this she has videos that really help to understand the process. Check it out if you get the chance.
