    % img/recipes/black.french.toast.1.jpg
    & Usually when I make french toast i'll just use a soy milk as a base. I made some though recently using The simple veganista's <a href=\"http://thesimpleveganista.blogspot.ca/2013/02/banana-french-toastyes-please.html\">Banana french toast</a> recipe thought the idea was brilliant and I do love bananas in my breakfasts SO i decided to try it out! By the way she also has a great 'orange french toast' recipe.
