      Olive oil : 1 1/2 tbsp
      Dijon mustard : 1/2 tsp
      Thyme : 1 tsp
      Balsamic vinegar : 1 tbsp
      Sea salt : Pinch
      Black pepper : Pinch 
    Latkes
      Potatoes : 2
      Yellow onions : 1
      Sea salt : pinch
      Black pepper : pinch
    Apple sauce
      Unsweetened apple sauce : 1/4 cup
      White miso : 1 1/2 tbsp
      Maple syrup : 1 tbsp
    Topping
      Scallions : 1 branch

ANISE BREAD WITH SWEET PEAR SAUCE
