      Soy yogurt : 2 tbsp
      Brown sugar : 1/3 cup
      Sugar : 1/3 cup
      Vanilla extract : 1 tsp
      Baking soda : 1/2 tsp
      Baking powder : 1/2 tsp
      Sea salt : 1/2 tsp
      Cocoa powder : 2 tbsp
      Oats : 1 1/2 cups, coarsely ground
